title: Maid’S Night
description:
Description :
        Read manhwa Maid's Night / The Maid's Night /  On the wedding night, the master's bride disappeared. In the empty princess's chamber, Evely stood at a loss until the master commanded: "You must take the princess's place." What began as a half-mocking game, the maid's boldness, despite her fear, aroused his cruel instincts. "Master" "Yes, I am your master." So, "Stick out your tongue calmly."
